  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we started to, to catch, to, to get ourselves on, on [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] passenger trains-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not on passenger, on transport trains, cattle trains, transport trains, all kind of trains, which was a very dangerous thing to do in Russia, especially at the wartime.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you were caught you could have got shot right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And to our luck we were, we were caught on the way, once by an [INAUDIBLE], and he, right away he wanted to part us with our mother, take our [INAUDIBLE] to the jail.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was sent away in some orphanage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we were-- my mother started to cry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We started to cry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then my mother said, you, you're going to take me and put me to jail?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My husband is on the front and fighting, and you're going to-- oh, your husband's on the front?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that saved us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he put us on passenger train all the way to, to our destination-- almost all the way to our destination.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this is how, actually, we arrived, so-- So we arrived there and then, again, started-- we-- our place was Samarkand in Uzbekistan.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we, we came there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And again, you have nowhere to stay and no food and that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we, we choose to go to a kolkhoz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Kolkhoz, that is a co-op, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] agricultural co-op.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "OK, let's stop here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
